{"text_id":116752,"tokens":["The"," Electoral"," College"," system"," in"," the"," United"," States"," has"," been"," a"," topic"," of"," intense"," debate"," for"," many"," years","."," This"," system",","," established"," by"," the"," Founding"," Fathers"," in"," the"," Constitution",","," was"," designed"," to"," provide"," a"," balance"," of"," power"," between"," small"," and"," large"," states"," in"," the"," election"," of"," the"," President"," of"," the"," United"," States","."," However",","," as"," the"," nation"," has"," evolved",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," has"," come"," under"," scrutiny"," for"," its"," advantages"," and"," disadvantages",".","\n\n","One"," of"," the"," primary"," advantages"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," is"," that"," it"," ensures"," that"," smaller"," states"," have"," a"," voice"," in"," the"," presidential"," election"," process","."," The"," system"," requires"," each"," state"," to"," have"," a"," minimum"," of"," three"," electoral"," votes",","," regardless"," of"," its"," population"," size","."," This"," guarantees"," that"," less"," populous"," states"," have"," a"," proportional"," say"," in"," the"," election",","," which"," helps"," to"," prevent"," the"," concentration"," of"," power"," in"," more"," populous"," states",".","\n\n","Another"," advantage"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," is"," that"," it"," provides"," a"," clear"," winner"," in"," the"," presidential"," election","."," In"," a"," system"," where"," the"," president"," is"," chosen"," by"," popular"," vote",","," there"," is"," a"," possibility"," that"," no"," candidate"," would"," receive"," a"," majority"," of"," the"," votes","."," This"," could"," result"," in"," a"," prolonged"," and"," contentious"," process"," to"," determine"," the"," next"," president","."," In"," contrast",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," provides"," a"," clear"," and"," decisive"," outcome"," in"," the"," election",".","\n\n","Despite"," these"," advantages",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," also"," has"," several"," disadvantages","."," One"," of"," the"," most"," significant"," disadvantages"," is"," that"," it"," can"," result"," in"," a"," situation"," where"," the"," winner"," of"," the"," popular"," vote"," does"," not"," become"," president","."," This"," has"," occurred"," five"," times"," in"," U",".","S","."," history",","," most"," recently"," in"," the"," ","2","0","0","0"," and"," ","2","0","1","6"," elections","."," This"," discrepancy"," between"," the"," popular"," vote"," and"," the"," electoral"," vote"," can"," undermine"," the"," legitimacy"," of"," the"," election"," process",".","\n\n","Another"," disadvantage"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," is"," that"," it"," encourages"," presidential"," candidates"," to"," focus"," their"," campaigns"," primarily"," on"," a"," handful"," of"," \"","battle","ground","\""," states","."," These"," states"," are"," considered"," critical"," to"," winning"," the"," election"," because"," of"," their"," relatively"," even"," distribution"," of"," electoral"," votes","."," As"," a"," result",","," candidates"," often"," overlook"," states"," with"," a"," clear"," majority"," of"," voters"," supporting"," one"," party",","," which"," can"," lead"," to"," a"," lack"," of"," representation"," and"," a"," feeling"," of"," dis","enf","ranch","isement"," for"," voters"," in"," those"," states",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," in"," the"," United"," States"," has"," both"," advantages"," and"," disadvantages","."," While"," it"," ensures"," that"," smaller"," states"," have"," a"," voice"," in"," the"," presidential"," election"," process"," and"," provides"," a"," clear"," winner",","," it"," can"," result"," in"," a"," discrepancy"," between"," the"," popular"," vote"," and"," the"," electoral"," vote",","," as"," well"," as"," a"," focus"," on"," battle","ground"," states"," to"," the"," detriment"," of"," others","."," Ultimately",","," the"," continuation"," of"," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," should"," be"," evaluated"," in"," the"," context"," of"," the"," nation","'","s"," values"," and"," priorities","."," If"," the"," goal"," is"," to"," ensure"," that"," every"," vote"," counts"," and"," that"," the"," president"," is"," chosen"," by"," a"," majority"," of"," voters",","," then"," a"," move"," towards"," a"," popular"," vote"," system"," may"," be"," warranted","."," However",","," if"," the"," goal"," is"," to"," balance"," the"," power"," between"," small"," and"," large"," states",","," then"," the"," Electoral"," College"," system"," may"," be"," the"," best"," option","."," In"," the"," end",","," the"," decision"," should"," be"," based"," on"," a"," thorough"," examination"," of"," the"," advantages"," and"," disadvantages"," of"," the"," system"," and"," the"," values"," that"," are"," most"," important"," to"," the"," nation","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}